body:
Hi all,
I have the following code to sort UNIX's password file, it works fine
but can only display on stdout. How can I make it write the output to
a file?
Thanks,

#!/bin/perl -w
#
use strict;
open(myFILE, '|-','awk','-F:','s[$1]++==0' ) or die $!;
open(passwdFH, "passwd");
while () { print myFILE; }
close(myFILE);


